name: Wesa Ready To Do Our-sa Part
Lore: 'Every Gungan that died on the battle plains gave Amidala and her troops that much more time to capture the Viceroy.',
Text: 'Deploy on table. If your Gungan was just lost from a site, may place him here. Once per battle, may place one of your Gungans here out of play to add 4 to your total power during that battle.',
